com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.container

Class DefaultPageShell

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.container.DefaultPageShell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PageShell

    public class DefaultPageShell
extends Object
implements PageShell

    A default implementation of the PageShell interface.

    This implementation writes the absolute minimum amount of mark-up necessary to support a WComponent application. There is no visible content written to the headers/footers.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Yiannis Paschalidis
